Rogue  2.0hp / level  (120 at 60th)<br>
Cleric  1.5hp / level  (90 at 60th)<br>
15 Sta at creation would be half these figures, etc...<br>
<br>
Truth is that it's not this linear, but we're all 60th in the end right?<br>
<br>
While this doesn't appear to be much, in the endgame it is commonly more difficult to max Sta than and other melee stat.  This means that pts put here are always good, even in a raid buff situation.<br>
<br>
